{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01ReiiSLnXTKHqyzGVQKZN42","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"基于对现有代码的探索，我来设计这两个签名。\n\n## 现有流程梳理\n\n`POST /api/v1/policy/apply-existing-entities` (在 PolicyController) 是现有的批量 reprocess 入口，流程是：\n1. `entityService.markAllForReprocess()` → 批量设 `reprocessState = INIT`\n2. 发布 `PolicyReprocessRequestedEvent` → 触发 `PolicyReprocessJob` 立即异步执行\n3. Job 每 30s 也会扫一次 INIT 实体\n\n新 endpoint 是**单个 entity** 版本，流程完全一样。\n\n---\n\n## 设计方案\n\n### `EntityService` 接口（新增）\n\n```java\n/**\n * Marks the entity as INIT to re-enter the policy reprocess pipeline.\n * Returns false if entity does not exist.\n */\nboolean reprocess(Long entityId);\n```\n\n### `EntityServiceImpl` 实现\n\n```java\n@Override\n@Transactional\npublic boolean reprocess(Long entityId) {\n    Entity entity = getById(entityId);\n    if (entity == null) {\n        return false;\n    }\n    return updateReprocessStateById(entityId, ReprocessState.INIT);\n}\n```\n\n`updateReprocessStateById` 已存在，直接复用。\n\n---\n\n### `EntityController` 新增 endpoint\n\n```java\n// 注入（与 PolicyController 对齐）\n@Resource\nprivate ApplicationEventPublisher eventPublisher;\n\n@PostMapping(\"/{id}/reprocess\")\npublic ResultDTO<Void> reprocessEntity(@PathVariable Long id) {\n    try {\n        boolean accepted = entityService.reprocess(id);\n        if (!accepted) {\n            return ResultDTO.error(/* entity-not-found error code */, \"entity not found: \" + id);\n        }\n        eventPublisher.publishEvent(new PolicyReprocessRequestedEvent(this, 1, \"api\"));\n        return ResultDTO.success(null);\n    } catch (Exception e) {\n        log.error(\"Failed to trigger reprocess for entity {}\", id, e);\n        return ResultDTO.error(/* internal error code */, e.getMessage());\n    }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 几个需要你确认的点\n\n| 问题 | 建议 |\n|------|------|\n| `ResultDTO.error()` 的错误码常量名 | 参照项目里 `ErrorCode` 或 `ResultCode` 里的 NOT_FOUND / INTERNAL_ERROR |\n| entity 在 `RUNNING` 时允许重新 mark INIT 吗？ | 目前设计无限制，与 `markAllForReprocess` 行为一致；如需保护可加 `reprocessState != RUNNING` 条件 |\n| 是否需要 request body | 目前不需要，与 `PolicyController` 的触发接口对齐 |\n| `PolicyReprocessRequestedEvent` 构造参数 | 需确认 `triggerSource` 用 `\"api\"` 还是有常量定义 |\n\n要我直接写入代码吗？"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":3492,"cache_read_input_tokens":17673,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":3492},"output_tokens":29,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"96ee62c5-d876-46ad-aa4f-f8b05d56b121","uuid":"90c83cb1-a0c7-47f7-8f49-0e86b2ce8323"}
